134lk8h6-3333.name: Mercedes Benz S 500
134lk8h6-3333.description: The 2022 Mercedes-Benz S-class is as much a personal limo for the ultra-wealthy as it is a rolling showcase of the company's latest tech. ... Along with standard all-wheel drive, the S-class's effortless acceleration comes from a 429-hp straight-six (S500) or a 496-hp V-8 (S580).

12c9sf49-4hzd.name: Audi A8
12c9sf49-4hzd.description: The Audi A8 is a full-size luxury sedan manufactured and marketed by the German automaker Audi since 1994. Succeeding the Audi V8, and now in its fourth generation, the A8 has been offered with both front- or permanent all-wheel drive—and in short- and long-wheelbase variants.

337e983b-b469.name: Kia Sorento
337e983b-b469.description: The Sorento is a seven-seat SUV with a second-row bench seat and two third-row seats. All models with the turbocharged engine have middle-row captain's chairs that turn this crossover into a six-person vehicle. The first two rows offer ample head- and legroom, and it's easy to find a comfortable sitting position.

0040221f-0ad2.name: Mercedes Benz G 63 AMG
0040221f-0ad2.description: The Mercedes-Benz G-Class, sometimes called G-Wagon (short for Geländewagen, "terrain vehicle"), is a four-wheel drive automobile manufactured by Magna Steyr (formerly Steyr-Daimler-Puch) in Austria and sold by Mercedes-Benz. ... The G-Wagon is characterised by its boxy styling and body-on-frame construction.
